<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <section style="padding: 4rem 0; margin-top: 80px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary);">About Sneaker Head</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Born in the streets, built for legends</p>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
                <div>
                    <h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our Story</h2>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        Founded by sneaker enthusiasts and tech innovators, Sneaker Head was born from a simple belief: 
                        footwear should be more than just functional—it should be transformational.
                    </p>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        We started with a vision to bridge the gap between street culture and luxury fashion. 
                        Today, we're proud to serve customers worldwide with our commitment to innovation, quality, and authentic style.
                    </p>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
                        Every pair tells a story of craftsmanship, technology, and the relentless pursuit of perfection. 
                        We don't just make shoes—we create experiences that elevate your journey.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <div style="width: 300px; height: 300px; background: var(--bg-secondary); border-radius: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <i class="fas fa-shoe-prints" style="font-size: 4rem; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
                <div style="background: var(--bg-secondary); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; text-align: center;">
                    <i class="fas fa-rocket" style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Innovation First</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Cutting-edge materials and smart technology integration in every design.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: var(--bg-secondary); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; text-align: center;">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart" style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Authentic Style</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Born from street culture, refined for luxury. Shoes that speak your language.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: var(--bg-secondary); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 1rem; text-align: center;">
                    <i class="fas fa-users" style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Community Driven</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Built by sneakerheads, for sneakerheads. Our community shapes every decision.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>